_sText:
My first ported map to CSS. 
Let me know if you want me to do anything different for the next map :)

Checklist:
64 spawns: Yes
Anglefixed: Yes
Bspzipped + compressed: Yes
Hookzones: Yes
Endzones pushed back 1 unit: Yes
Visuals tested on CSS: Yes
Surf tested on Momentum Mod: Yes

Surf_santorini2_ksf is a bit different to the CSGO version. I'm used to mapping on CSGO when you can scroll models. So when porting it I couldn't find the right models so I changed a few of them. So the visuals are somewhat the same but it's not identical.

Surf_santorini2_ksf | Tier 3 | 66.7 Tick | 1 Bonus | 4 Checkpoints

Zoners & Admins:

b1s - b1e
startzone - endzone
CP1 - CP2 - CP3 - CP4

Any issues please let me know. 

Enjoy!

Yours,
twitch.tv/quethesurfer.
